  "title": "Customer Service cum Warehouse Assistant (Central) DT",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><p><ul><li>Provide excellent customer service at the collection counter, including order issuance and customer inquiries</li><li>Handle product exchanges accurately and efficiently in accordance with company policies</li><li>Assist with general warehouse and operational duties as required</li><li>Perform ad-hoc tasks assigned by the supervisor to support daily operations</li></ul></p><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><p><ul><li>Minimum GCE ‘O’ Level qualification</li><li>Strong interpersonal and communication skills</li><li>Pleasant and customer-oriented personality</li><li>Able to work well in a team and in a fast-paced environment</li></ul><p>Attention to: Debbie Tan | 82115165</p><p>By submitting any application or résumé to us, you will be deemed to have agreed and consented to us disclosing your personal information to prospective employers for their consideration.<br /><br />We regret to inform you that only shortlisted candidates will be notified. All applications will be treated with the strictest confidence.<br /><br />Elitez Pte Ltd | EA Licence: 16C8004| Hailey YANG | Registrations No: R1876431</p></p>",
